Dismantler requests general information about the individual vehicle and its components via VIN
Dismantler selects one component for detailed information and analysis
Data Provisioning of Component and Material
Assistant requests detailed information about the component and contained materials
Assistant calculates the technical feasibility of different R
Strategies for the component based on standardized decision log
Assistant calculates environmental impact of different (technically feasible) R
Strategies based on an LCA of subsequent proc
esses and recommends an optimal R
Assistant updates Digital Twin of component with calculation result and selected R
strategy to allow for further monitoring,
digital traceability for second life and feedback to design.
